data.description: This home is move in ready. New duct system, paint, interior doors, water heater, washing machine, backsplash, and refrigerator are just some of the amenities included. There are two living areas, 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, and a fireplace. Outdoors there are pomegranate trees, mature trees, large backyard, a trampoline, newly added rocks in the front yard for a low maintenance EZ-scape. This home is ready for you to make your own memories!
